    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong> and <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs or until the spices are fragrant</p>",
